PM Indiya ya halarci wurin haikali a wurin da aka yi jayayya
NEW Delhi (AP) - Firayim Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin karya kasa a wata mai zuwa don haikalin Hindu a kan wani wurin da aka yi jayayya a arewacin Indiya inda wani masallaci na karni na 16 ya tsage daga masu bin hindu a 1992, bisa ga amincewar da ke kula da gina haikalin.
An shirya bikin ne don watan Augus. 5, kwanan wata masu shirya taron sun ce an yi amfani da ilmin sararin samaniya ga Hindus amma wannan yana da alama a shekara guda tun lokacin da majalisar Indiya ta soke matsayin da ta fi rinjaye na jihar Musulmi kawai, Jammu da Kashmir.
Alamar ba za ta yiwu ba a rasa magoya baya da abokan hamayyar Modi ta Hindu ta kasa Bharatiya Janata Party, ko BJP, wanda manifesto ya yi shekaru da suka gabata ya hada da alkawuran tsallake mulkin Kashmir da kuma gina haikali ga ubangiji na Hindu Ram inda masallacin Mughal-era ya tsaya, wani shafin a cikin Birnin Ayodhya da ke Uttar Pradesh jihar cewa masu kishin addini sun yi imani da zama wurin haihuwar Ram.
Saboda coronavirus har yanzu yana raguwa a fadin Indiya, wanda ya ba da rahoto na uku mafi girma a duniya, za a watsa bikin a kan talabijin na jihar kuma adadin mahalarta da masu kallo za su iyakance, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko Kungiyar Hindu ta Duniya, a Hindu Ƙungiyoyi masu kishin ƙasa sun haɗu da BJP.
Haikalin zai zama “wata cibiya mai dorewa da rashin mutuwa ta hanyar jituwar zamantakewa, hadin kan kasa da hadewa da kuma tada hankalin Hindutva,” ko kuma hanyar rayuwa ta Hindu, inji mai magana da yawun kungiyar Vinod Bansal ya fada a cikin wata sanarwar labarai da ya fitar ranar Asabar.
