'Yan sanda uku sun samu raunuka, ciki har da wanda aka kwantar da shi a asibiti tare da rauni a kafa sanadiyyar wata fashewa, kuma an kama masu zanga-zanga 16 da sanyin safiyar jiya, in ji 'yan sandan.
