Bipasha Mukherjee, 52, na Kirkland, Wash., ta ce ta yi zanga-zanga a kan tituna tun watan Mayu kuma ta ce yana damuwa da ita ganin irin wannan mummunar dabara da 'yan sanda ke yi.
“Wannan ba ita ce kasar da na yi hijira zuwa ba,” in ji Misis Mukherjee, wacce ta isa daga Indiya fiye da shekaru 30 da suka wuce.
