Kokarin da duniya ke yi na samar da magunguna masu amfani da covid ke hankoron Amurka saboda masu bincike suna gwada kwayoyi a “hanyar da ba ta dace ba, mai son zuciya,” masanin da ke jagorantar shirin Birtaniya ya yi gargadin.
Shirin gwajin farfadowa da Birtaniya, wanda ya shafi marasa lafiya 12,000 a asibitocin Birtaniya ɗari, ya riga ya nuna alamar sabon magani don magance cutar kuma ya nuna wasu biyu - a baya ana tunanin su zama masu ceton rai - a matsayin marasa amfani.
