Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya zargi sakataren yada labarai na White House Kayleigh McEnDuk da damuwa da kafofin watsa labarai ta hanyar yi mata bayani game da siyasa maimakon bayani - a bayyane yake manta cewa masu rahoto sun zabi tambayoyin.
Wani labarin ranar Asabar da AP, mafi girma kamfanin dillancin labarai na Amurka, ya ce bayanin labaran White House na iya zama “karya al'adar,” kamar yadda Mcenany ya sanya su “wani tsari, mai cikakkiyar talla ga shugaban da ke fuskantar sake zaben, wani wuri don kai hare-hare a kan kafofin watsa labarai da kuma dandalin da ya fi haske a kan bayani” game da abin da gwamnati take yi.
