Ted Cruz ya ce manufofin Pelosi su ne “tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka”
Washington - Sanata Ted Cruz na Texas ya zargi Kakakin Majalisa Nancy Pelosi da House Democrats da tura wani kunshin taimako na coronavirus wanda ke mayar da hankali kan “tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka” yayin da tattaunawa a mataki na gaba ke ci gaba.
A cikin wata hira da “Face the Nation” a ranar Lahadi, Cruz ya ce kasar tana fuskantar matsalolin biyu a lokaci guda: wata annoba ta duniya da ta yi ikirarin rayukan mutane fiye da 600,000 a duniya da kuma “cikakkiyar masifa ta tattalin arziki” a Amurka.
Amma Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wanda ya bayyana a kan “Face the Nation” gaban sanata, "yana “mayar da hankali ga ba daga cikin wadanda ba.”
“Manufofinta suna nuna tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka,” in ji Texas Republican.
“Kuma musamman ma, ka kalli takardar Naira tiriliyan 3 da take kokarin turawa, kawai tana fallasa kudi ne ga abokanta kuma ba a zahiri warware matsalar ba. Manufarmu ya kamata Amurkawa su so su dawo aiki. Suna so su iya azurta wa iyalinsu.”
'Yan majalisar dattijai Republicans da fadar White House sun shafe makon jiya suna tattaunawa kan sharuddan karo na hudu na martanin coronavirus, inda suke sa ran kashe dala tiriliyan 1.
A karshen mako, shugaban ma'aikata na White House Mark Meadows da sakataren baitulmalin Steven Mnuchin sun gangara zuwa Capitol Hill don karin tattaunawa da ma'aikatan majalisar dattijai, kuma Mnuchin ya gaya wa Fox News a wata hira da aka yi ranar Lahadi an tsara cikakkun bayanai da za a bayyana daga shugaban masu rinjaye Mitch McConnell a ranar Litinin.
Batun da ya fi damuwa ga masu shari'a - da kuma batun jayayya tsakanin 'yan Republicans da Democrats - shi ne karewar ingantaccen amfanin rashin aikin yi, wanda ya fara tafiya a wannan karshen mako.
Duk da yake Democrats so “lokaci hudu” coronavirus kunshin don ci gaba da $600 bunkasa ga amfanin, Republicans suna kira a gare shi ya zama pared baya kuma suna jayayya da wasu Amurkawa suna yin karin daga rashin aikin yi fiye da yadda suka yi a albashi.
Cruz ya ce fiye da rabin Amurkawa da ke karbar ingantaccen aikin yi an biya su fiye da lokacin da suke aiki kuma ya ce ya yi magana da kananan masu kasuwanci a Texas wadanda ke fama da matsala wajen sake dawo da ma'aikata.
“Ko shakka babu, ba za su dawo ba saboda gwamnatin tarayya tana biyan su, a wasu lokutan, sau biyu da yawa kudi su zauna gida,” inji shi.
Cruz ya ce majalisa ya kamata ta mayar da hankali ga wucewa a dawo da lissafin da zai sa ya fi sauƙi ga Amurkawa su koma aiki ta hanyar sauƙaƙe haraji da dokoki a kan ƙananan kasuwanni: “maimakon kawai nuna triliyan daga ƙofar, lissafin dawowa zai dakatar da biyan haraji, wanda zai ba shi biyan kuɗi zuwa kowa da kowa a Amurka wanda ke aiki. Wannan a zahiri yana sa mutane su koma aiki,” inji shi.
Shugaba Trump ya bukaci a makon da ya gabata kunshin agajin da ya hada da yanke haraji, amma Mnuchin ya ce ba zai kasance cikin dokokin ba, kamar yadda kudirin ya yi rashin karbuwa a tsakanin 'yan Republicans.
Mista Trump ya amince da yanke harajin zai kasance ba daga lissafi na gaba amma ya nemi fil zargi akan 'yan Democrats.
Cruz, wanda a makon da ya gabata ya ki amincewa da kudin kunshin mai zuwa, ya ce Lahadi ba ya cikin jirgi tare da awo daga 'yan uwansa Senate Republicans.
Amma kuma ya soki lissafin dala tiriliyan 3 da majalisar mai kula da democradiya ta shige a watan Mayu inda ya zargi abokan adawar sa na siyasa da gangan wajen aikata wani matakin da zai lalata shugaban kasar gabanin zaben watan Nuwamba.
“Manufar Democrats kawai ita ce kayar da Donald Trump, kuma sun yanke shawarar hanya mafi kyau don kayar da Donald Trump an rufe kowane kasuwanci a Amurka, rufe kowace makaranta a Amurka,” in ji shi.
“Ka sani, Nancy Pelosi tayi magana game da aiki maza da mata. Abin da ta ke ba da shawara shi ne kiyaye aiki maza da mata daga aiki.”
