Kusan kusan watanni uku a cikin tsauni na Ladakh ya yi ikirarin rayukan fiye da 500 sojojin Indiya.
Tun da farko a yau, ministan tsaro Rajnath Singh, da karamin minista Shripad Naik, Babban Jami'in Tsaro Janar Bipin Rawat, Babban Jami'in Soja Janar M Naravane, Air Chief Marshal R K S Bhadauria da kuma Navy Chief Admiral Karambir Singh ma sun biya kudin bautar kasar Amar Jawan Jyoti.
